[IMG]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/3984/34913244.png[/IMG]

This is a modification based on ENBseries 0.099beta created by Boris Vorontsov.
This ENBseries, has a different palette, totally appropriate for Skyrim, the graphics settings were adjusted to provide a new atmosphere for Skyrim.

[IMG]http://img821.imageshack.us/img821/1435/65941356.png[/IMG]

Installation is simple and uncomplicated, just copy the files that are zipped to the folder where your game is installed.

[IMG]http://img440.imageshack.us/img440/4615/83898262.png[/IMG]

Just delete the files that you copied to the folder where your game was installed.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Thank you all!
